2. Make a representation with the respective banks to establish and enroll for a separate bank account to accommodate all electronic payments to statutory agencies and other transactions related thereto. Moreover, subsidiary ledgers must also be maintained under the Cash in Bank account for each statutory agency (e.g. BIR Subsidiary Ledger, HDMF Subsidiary Ledger, etc) for easier monitoring and reconciliation of bank accommodation of electronic payment remittances;
